sections.heading: to 63-6-7 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1998, ch. 108, § 81 repealed 63-6-1 to 63-6-7 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1878, ch. 1, tit. 9, §§ 4-10, relating to voluntary dissolution and venue, effective January 1, 1999. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1998 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
